  "system": {
    "description": {
      "value": "<p><strong>Level 4</strong> Enchantment</p>\n<p><strong>Casting Time:</strong> 1 action</p>\n<p><strong>Range:</strong> 30 feet</p>\n<p><strong>Components:</strong> V, S</p>\n<p><strong>Duration:</strong> 1 hour</p>\n\nOne creature you can see within range makes a Wisdom saving throw. It does so with Advantage|XPHB if you or your allies are fighting it. On a failed save, the target has the Charmed|XPHB condition until the spell ends or until you or your allies damage it. The Charmed|XPHB creature is Friendly [Attitude]|XPHB|Friendly to you. When the spell ends, the target knows it was Charmed|XPHB by you.\n\n<p><strong>At Higher Levels:</strong> You can target one additional creature for each spell slot level above 4.</p>",
